data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT ON EXQUISITE LUXURY ESTATE! This coveted David Weekley Tranquility model, built in 2022, offers over 3700 square feet with 5 bedrooms, 3.5 baths & a 3 car garage! Upon entry you will immediately sense the spaciousness & open concept floorplan with soaring ceilings, attention to detail, & custom lighting throughout. The designer kitchen offers 2 toned shaker cabinets that run floor to ceiling, quartz countertops, a large island, & a perfectly positioned butlers pantry. This floorplan is INCREDIBLE! The Primary retreat offers a large Primary Bath with a modern soaking tub, large walk in shower and TWO massive walk-in closets with the laundry room conveniently attached! Every square inch of this home is masterfully planned & beautifully design
